Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與第二月亮對接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用其動力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再度發射迪格瑪Xenon炮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始準備
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 戰場情況混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在發射不免殃及友軍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為實現計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不惜付出任何犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按我說得辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉·格拉密斯 準備發射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉·格拉密斯開始變形了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到底想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特大人描繪的伊甸藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓將其化為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續前進 沿途支援友軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破當前宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬納森 不許哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓隊長的犧牲白費嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊潰維甘陣線！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後備動力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就用上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 我知道你很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除維生系統外 停止其他系統供應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力維持最大航速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士隊 迎擊側方來敵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與敵人陷入混戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看準了是敵人再打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達孜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手下的將士們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你皆有相同的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請堅信自己腳下的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你創建伊甸的決心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該是你發自內心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎麼了 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子不惜大義滅親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成 因為這點事就縮了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無路可退…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有通向伊甸之路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人 有何吩咐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉姆 把高達引到迪格瑪Xenon炮的射線軸上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和天神號一道 一舉殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同高達…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他們的突進企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扼殺聯邦的勝機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這場戰鬥結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 傑哈特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷伊爾 我去引出高達
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白這個命令意味著什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服從這個命令 就意味著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少記住那些陣亡者的姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣善良體貼的傑哈特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想像過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們即將營造的 伊甸中的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸是 他的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我最重要的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人就能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做回那個體貼善良的傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了保護他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護他善良的心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探測系統反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方路線上出現敵艦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右滿舵 避讓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人突然發什麼神經？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄恩 我會阻止這場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 進籠子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡之籠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達 要不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用來結束戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 錐炮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你壞傑哈特大人的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開 臭海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷伊爾 你不該來這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早有心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 雷伊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種恐怖的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即呼叫奧克拉姆德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有回答 再次呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底打得什麼算盤 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們又要使用要塞炮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種武器不是不可能短時間連射嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢在戰場上進行那種變形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中必有緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾倫格雷亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人要塞會不會從第二月亮獲取能量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為光束炮充能？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅從熱感器上觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法排除這種可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 亂戰情況下發射…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算以自己人為代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶走高達和天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記 對手是維甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼立即下令避讓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 天神號只要繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就會盯住這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以天神號為餌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓其他艦艇離開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲自己人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特他竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起 天神號乘員集體離艦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 離開天神號？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下 出去也會被敵人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在這裏也是被打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經要求他們營救撤離的乘員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營救？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 準備撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立即前往第三格納庫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE-1 Gransa 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:11:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘員馬上就要離艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引敵人火力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄天神號？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧布萊特 喬納森
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉來遲了 明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就這樣跳進宇宙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令說不要上逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們在甲板待命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我們上海盜船？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別指望敵人的探測器是瞎子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 登上海盜船巴洛諾克號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還算順利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老夥計 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家抓緊DarkHunter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用超級推進器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣離開敵人的射線軸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪裏也別想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷伊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到最後一刻不許離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以免敵人察覺我們的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 我竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這種…被這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷伊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 看我為你報仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬納森
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家抓住DarkHunter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧布萊特先生 請快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不放過它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 雜兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再垂死掙扎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級推進器準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點火倒計時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 點火同時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也用最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只當輔助推進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧布萊特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們走…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼 奧布萊特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要…活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能來找你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧布萊特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三台高達全部在射程範圍以內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉姆 芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道道歉也無法得到原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓計劃成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多勒的在天之靈安息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再提哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠… 在您手下戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我最大的光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉姆 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓伊甸 回到我們手中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你保證
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要踏上伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特 你這該死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍戰艦 擊沉5艘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲了自己最忠誠的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈有不成之理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是高達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底…在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底幹了些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想勝過我這個哥哥 不是那塊料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太難看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那塊料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要擊落高達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏下這場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人從法·扎德上出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特 不惜犧牲部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要實現夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已經放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人性的大義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何價值可言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂個屁！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸不是為了讓人活得更有人樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為伊甸獻出了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無怨無悔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切…都在逝去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…握不住它…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會有把握不住的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多次放走我這個敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明作為戰士之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你首先是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特大人的…夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的…夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則… 我們是為何而活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你們度過的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士社團的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段時光是何等的充實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定…嫉妒過我的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在羨慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…想與愛人生兒育女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你那樣…生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 這下可以優勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 太厲害了傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次多虧你 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧…我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有你才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你才有現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.42,0:22:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫長的戰鬥正在等待結束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 三個人的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.93,0:24:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否能夠打開未來之扉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.71,0:24:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士高達AGE 最終話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.77,0:24:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫長旅途的終點

